author: J14T14
title: This "Special Offer" Does Not Have Special Value
review: This set is not as special as it may seem on the box. There are no special parts (all are quite common) and the builds on the front of the box are not that appealing. There is not too much to say about this set. It is not a fantastic set and it just seems like it was a parts pack that was given the label of "Special Offer" just to make it sell better.
